original_title: iHeartRadio Jingle Ball 2016: Z100's Jingle Ball Live From Madison Square Garden
overview: Elvis Duran hosts this concert from Madison Square Garden. Among those scheduled to perform are Justin Bieber, Ariana Grande, Fifth Harmony, Diplo, Charlie Puth, Lukas Graham, DNCE and Niall Horan.
